{"type": "article", "id": 12743, "title": "Peak Design 可伸展的相机包", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-29T06:36:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606002557oncjvxlSqQR3H7hb.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tPeak Design 的这一款包据说是 Kickstarter 上面有史以来卖得最好的一款包，这款包包由 Peak Design 和 “互联网最红摄影师” Trey Ratcliff 合作完成，可以从 13.5 升伸展到 20.5 升，也就从一个普通的背包变成了一个相机包。包包内部有着大量的可折叠分层设计，同时外部防水层和内部的绒毛为物品带来双重的防护。目前他们在 Kickstarter 上已经拿到超过 200 万美元，这是<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/peak-design/the-everyday-messenger-a-bag-for-cameras-and-essen\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140445Mw3jclgRve0KaPEh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261404453sIVqeTrcJlnbLSO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140447gAvqlGQsUkod9yOV.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140448gsDmzSidr4AOavqQ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69264706\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140450sS7eF9vEqnimGC6x.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140452jhH59naS6NsAKWgF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140453fyp4cQ3X2dv9bxwj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66602317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140454dYNB6kJwM5FigXtr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66513761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140455pSx9yCjOvGYd5le7.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}